video.title: Highlight: Twitch Plays (Viewers play/Chat plays) "Super Mario 64" on a real N64 console, type "!help" to learn how to play

message.body: @jerick_i Valid inputs are A, B, Z, L, R, Start, CUp, CDown, CLeft, CRight (C buttons), DUp, DDown, DLeft, DRight (D-Pad, unused in most games), Up, Down, Left and Right (Analog stick, used in almost every game as the standard movement input). Typos
